<author>Francesco Testa</author>
<title>Psalm 37:4</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 My Lord you are the one and only God
 My Lord you see what no one else can see
 And You alone have loved me so my Lord
 Before Your throne I'll fall face to the ground

[V2]
 I worship you with all I have in me
 I'll offer you this sacrifice with joy
 And I belong to You
 And I belong to You

[V3]
 I'm here to find Your joy
 I'm here to find Your desire
 I'm here to find Your mercies God
 I'm here to find You Jesus

[V4]
 Delight Yourself in Me
 I'll give you your true desire
 Commit your way to Me
 Have faith that I will do this
 And your reward will shine like the dawn

[V5]
 Your vindication like the noonday sun
 Your vindication like the noonday sun
 So watch Me as I do this son

[V6]
 I worship you with all I have in me
 I'll offer you this sacrifice with joy
 And I belong to You
 And I belong to You

[V7]
 I'm here to find Your joy
 I'm here to find Your desire
 I'm here to find Your mercies God
 I'm here to find You Jesus

[V8]
 My God I want to worship You
 To worship You day by day
 My God I want to please You
 To worship You with all I do

[V9]
 Delight Yourself in Me
 I'll give you your true desire
 Commit your way to Me
 Have faith that I will do this
 And your reward will shine like the dawn
 And your reward will shine like the dawn

[V10]
 Your vindication like the noonday sun
 Your vindication like the noonday sun
 So watch Me as I do this son

[V11]
 You're my delight my Lord
 You're my delight my King
 You are my Healer
 You're my Savior</lyrics>
</song>